Title: An Act Changing the Names of the Calumbuyan I Barrio School and Calumbuyan Ii Barrio School Both in Barangay Santa Ana, Municipality of Calatagan, Province of Batangas, to Pedro Palacio, Sr. Memorial Barrio School I and Pedro Palacio, Sr. Memorial Barrio School Ii, Respectively
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 842
An Act Changing the Names of the Calumbuyan I Barrio School and Calumbuyan Ii Barrio School Both in Barangay Santa Ana, Municipality of Calatagan, Province of Batangas, to Pedro Palacio, Sr. Memorial Barrio School I and Pedro Palacio, Sr. Memorial Barrio School Ii, Respectively
Section 1. The names of the Calumbuyan I Barrio School and Calumbuyan II Barrio School both in Barangay Santa Ana, Municipality of Calatagan, Province of Batangas are changed to Pedro Palacio, Sr. Memorial Barrio School I and Pedro Palacio, Sr. Memorial Barrio School II, respectively.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
